PLEASE HELP FEED THE CHILDREN of Liberia


https://www.gofundme.com/f/r5sfms-feed-the-children?utm_source=customer&utm_medium=copy_link-tip&utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet



Due to the COVID-19 crisis, many parents in Liberia are unable to work until the month of July. The government isn't giving out social benefits or living assistance. Due to this, many families are in a panic as they wouldn't be able to feed their children for the next 4 months. Banks in the country are also refusing to give out loans. Food prices are skyrocketing and getting more and more unaffordable. Your donation will be used to buy bags of rice that will then be sent to different communities throughout Monrovia, predominantly the poor communities. With the help of my team in Monrovia, each house will receive two bags of rice, which will last for about one month. I'm hoping to also reach villages in the interiors of Liberia with enough findings.
